This representation of the thesaurus follows the Simple Knowledge Organization System (SKOS) data model and has Resource Description Framework (RDF) syntax. This file gives a snapshot of the thesaurus as of the date tagged in the SKOS ConceptScheme. Additional documentation as well as archived, static versions of the thesaurus are available at: https://www.ncei.noaa.gov/access/paleo-search/study/31892. Please cite the preceding URL, the publication listed at that URL, and the date accessed when referencing the thesaurus.
